      ******************************************************************        
       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.                                                 
       PROGRAM-ID.             PMKUT096.                                        
       AUTHOR.                 AMANDA NEWHART                                   
       INSTALLATION.           KOHLS DEPARTMENT STORES.                         
       DATE-WRITTEN.           APRIL 2003.                                      
       DATE-COMPILED.                                                           
      ******************************************************************        
      *                                                                *        
      *    PMKUT096 -                                                  *        
      *      LOG ONTO ORACLE.  FIND THE CLEARANCE RECORDS FROM THE     *        
      *      SLS_RSLT_LOD TABLE.  LOAD THOSE RECORDS INTO THE          *        
      *      MDSE_LNE_CLRNC_FCT TABLE.  WHEN ALL THE CLEARANCE RECORDS *        
      *      HAVE BEEN SELECTED & INSERTED LOOK FOR THE TIERED RECORDS *        
      *      FROM THE SLS_RSLT_LOD TABLE.  INSERT THOSE RECORDS INTO   *        
      *      THE MDSE_SELN_LNE_TIER_FCT TABLE.  WHEN ALL THE TIERED    *        
      *      RECORDS HAVE BEEN SELECTED AND INSERTERD DO A COMMIT TO   *        
      *      MAKE SURE ALL THE INSERTS STAY.  THEN DISPLAY A COUNT OF  *        
      *      WHAT WAS FOUND AND INSERTED.                              *        
      *                                                                *        
      ******************************************************************        
      **   CHANGE LOG:                                                 *        
      ******************************************************************        
      *    07/17/2003 - AMANDA NEWHART - WR21770                       *        
      *     - DO NOT ABEND WHEN THE SALES DATE FILE IS EMPTY.  JUST    *        
      *       DISPLAY A MESSAGE INSTEAD.                               *        
      *                                                                *        
      *    08/05/2003 - COLLEEN CUMMINGS - P000572233                  *        
      *     - ABENDED ON TRYING TO FETCH INTO A VARIABLE NOT DEFINED   *        
      *       WITH A SIGN (PV-MKDN-RTL-AMT WAS NEGATIVE - BUT GOING    *        
      *       INTO A 9(10)V99 FIELD). CHANGED ALL THE PV- AMT FIELDS   *        
      *       TO BE S9(08)V99 COMP-3 INSTEAD.                          *        
      *       "ORA-24355: ATTEMPT TO STORE A NEGATIVE NUMBER IN AN     *        
      *       UNSIGNED DISPLAY..."                                     *        
      *                                                                *        
      *    07/30/2018 - COGNIZANT - CHG0204126                         *        
      *     - ORACLE LOGON STANDARDS PROGRAM CHANGE                    *        
      ******************************************************************        
      ******************************************************************        
